it.emarolab.sit

Interface SITBase.VOCABOLARY

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    SITBase.CLASS, SITBase.DATA_PROPERTY, SITBase.INDIVIDUAL, SITBase.OBJECT_PROPERTY
    Enclosing interface:
    SITBase

    public static interface SITBase.VOCABOLARY
    The base interface for the SIT constants.

    This interface is aimed to be a container for all the String constants used in the ontology. It is extended in order to give a clear semantic to the constants by a name space.
    Those names are tuned with respect to the t-box ontology representation used by the SIT algorithm (available at: SITBase.ONTO_FILE)

    File: it.emarolab.sit.SITBase
